PersonalMission.Name: TD-1: Effective Performance
PersonalMission.Description: Tank destroyers are a great choice for players who like to destroy enemy vehicles from a distance.
PersonalMission.Hint: Tank destroyers have serious firepower, but most are relatively fragile. Try engaging from long range—the accuracy of your gun allows for this.

Primary.Conditions: •  Be among the top 3 players on your team by experience earned
